            . I know this reticule and its contents to be mine; it has the property stated in it - it was in our carriage, which is an open chariot; we were standing up to look at the King, and this laid on the seat; the officer brought it back to me.</p>
               <p>The prisoner handed in a petition for mercy, pleading extreme distress.</p>
